"    Varicella",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 339px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This photomicrograph of the skin from a patient with varicella shows an intraepidermal vesicle. Multinucleated giant cells and nuclear inclusions are present.",
